<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>NAVLYS · Simulateur — argent de démonstration</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;500;600&family=Fraunces:ital,wght@0,500;1,400&family=Lora:wght@400;500&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js@4.4.0/dist/chart.umd.min.js"></script>
<style>
  :root {
    --ice: #7DD3FC;
    --ice-soft: #BAE6FD;
    --ice-glow: rgba(125,211,252,0.25);
    --black: #000;
    --black-card: #0F0F12;
    --line: rgba(125,211,252,0.12);
    --line-strong: rgba(125,211,252,0.25);
    --text: #F0F9FF;
    --text-soft: #CBD5E1;
    --text-mute: #64748B;
    --gold: #E8D4A2;
    --green: #86EFAC;
    --red: #FCA5A5;
    --serif-display: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    --serif-italic: 'Fraunces', serif;
    --serif-body: 'Lora', Georgia, serif;
    --mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  }
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    font-family: var(--serif-body);
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.65;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%,100% { opacity: 1 } 50% { opacity: 0.85 } }
  @keyframes glow { 0%,100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 var(--ice-glow); } 50% { box-shadow: 0 0 40px 6px var(--ice-glow); } }
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at top left, rgba(125,211,252,0.06), transparent 40%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom right, rgba(125,211,252,0.04), transparent 50%);
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .wrap { max-width: 1380px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px 24px 80px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 36px; }
  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--ice);
    letter-spacing: 0.32em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  }
  .eyebrow::before, .eyebrow::after { content: ''; width: 32px; height: 1px; background: var(--ice); }
  h1 {
    font-family: var(--serif-display);
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 52px); font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  h1 em { font-family: var(--serif-italic); font-style: italic; color: var(--ice); font-weight: 500; }
  header p { color: var(--text-soft); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; font-size: 16px; }

  /* === Layout principal : colonne gauche curseurs · droite résultats === */
  .layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 340px 1fr;
    gap: 28px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 980px) { .layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .panel {
    background: var(--black-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 24px;
  }
  .panel h2 {
    font-family: var(--serif-display);
    font-size: 22px; font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ice); margin-bottom: 18px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); padding-bottom: 10px;
  }

  /* === Curseurs === */
  .ctrl-group { margin-bottom: 22px; }
  .ctrl-label {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline;
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10.5px; color: var(--text-mute);
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.14em; margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .ctrl-label .val { color: var(--ice); font-weight: 500; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0; }
  .ctrl-label .val strong { color: var(--text); font-size: 15px; }
  input[type="range"] {
    -webkit-appearance: none; appearance: none;
    width: 100%; height: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--ice) 0%, var(--ice) var(--p,50%), rgba(125,211,252,0.15) var(--p,50%), rgba(125,211,252,0.15) 100%);
    border-radius: 999px; outline: none; cursor: pointer;
  }
  input[type="range"]::-webkit-slider-thumb {
    -webkit-appearance: none; appearance: none;
    width: 18px; height: 18px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--ice); cursor: grab;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(125,211,252,0.18);
    transition: transform 0.15s;
  }
  input[type="range"]::-webkit-slider-thumb:active { transform: scale(1.18); cursor: grabbing; }
  input[type="range"]::-moz-range-thumb {
    width: 18px; height: 18px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--ice); cursor: grab; border: none;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(125,211,252,0.18);
  }
  .ctrl-hint { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-mute); margin-top: 4px; }

  /* === Profil switcher === */
  .profil-switch {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 6px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    padding: 4px; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 22px;
  }
  .profil-btn {
    background: transparent; border: none; padding: 10px 6px;
    color: var(--text-mute); cursor: pointer;
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px;
    border-radius: 8px; transition: all 0.25s;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }
  .profil-btn.active.zen      { background: rgba(134,239,172,0.2); color: var(--green); }
  .profil-btn.active.precision{ background: rgba(125,211,252,0.2); color: var(--ice); }
  .profil-btn.active.boost    { background: rgba(232,212,162,0.2); color: var(--gold); }
  .profil-btn:hover { color: var(--text); }

  /* === Résultats === */
  .results-row {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 700px) { .results-row { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  .stat {
    background: var(--black-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 14px; padding: 18px;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-mute);
    letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .stat-value {
    font-family: var(--serif-display); font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.05;
  }
  .stat-value.big { font-size: 34px; }
  .stat-value em { font-family: var(--serif-italic); font-style: italic; color: var(--ice); }
  .stat-value.pos { color: var(--green); }
  .stat-value.neg { color: var(--red); }
  .stat-sub {
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-mute);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .stat-sub.pos { color: var(--green); } .stat-sub.neg { color: var(--red); }

  /* === Onglets graphiques === */
  .tabs {
    display: flex; gap: 4px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    padding: 4px; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .tab {
    flex: 1; background: transparent; border: none;
    padding: 12px 14px; color: var(--text-mute); cursor: pointer;
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 11px;
    border-radius: 8px; transition: all 0.25s;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .tab.active { background: rgba(125,211,252,0.15); color: var(--ice); }
  .tab:hover { color: var(--text); }

  /* === Chart wrapper === */
  .chart-box {
    background: var(--black-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 18px; padding: 20px;
    min-height: 380px;
  }
  .chart-canvas { width: 100% !important; height: 360px !important; }

  /* === Profil cards === */
  .profil-detail {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(125,211,252,0.05), transparent);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 14px; padding: 16px 20px; margin-top: 14px;
    font-size: 13.5px; color: var(--text-soft);
  }
  .profil-detail strong { color: var(--ice); }
  .profil-detail.zen { border-color: rgba(134,239,172,0.3); background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(134,239,172,0.05), transparent); }
  .profil-detail.zen strong { color: var(--green); }
  .profil-detail.boost { border-color: rgba(232,212,162,0.3); background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(232,212,162,0.05), transparent); }
  .profil-detail.boost strong { color: var(--gold); }

  /* === Disclaimer === */
  .disclaimer {
    margin-top: 30px;
    background: rgba(125,211,252,0.04);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px 20px;
    font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--text-mute);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .disclaimer strong { color: var(--ice); }

  /* === Quick presets === */
  .presets {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .preset {
    background: rgba(125,211,252,0.06); border: 1px solid var(--line);
    color: var(--text-soft); padding: 5px 10px;
    border-radius: 999px; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10px;
    cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }
  .preset:hover { background: rgba(125,211,252,0.18); color: var(--ice); border-color: var(--ice); }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

<header>
  <div class="eyebrow">NAVLYS NEXT GEN INVEST · Simulateur officiel</div>
  <h1>Joue avec ton avenir <em>financier</em>.</h1>
  <p>Curseurs interactifs · 5 ans de données réelles Yahoo Finance · stratégie SOL+NVDA+AVGO validée sur 357 simulations.</p>
</header>

<div class="layout">

  <!-- ==================== PANNEAU DE CONTRÔLE ==================== -->
  <div class="panel">

    <h2>🎚️ Tes paramètres</h2>

    <!-- Profil -->
    <div class="ctrl-group">
      <div class="ctrl-label">PROFIL D'INVESTISSEMENT</div>
      <div class="profil-switch">
        <button class="profil-btn zen" data-profil="Zen">🛡️ Zen</button>
        <button class="profil-btn precision active" data-profil="Précision">🎯 Précision</button>
        <button class="profil-btn boost" data-profil="Boost">🚀 Boost</button>
      </div>
      <div id="profilDetail" class="profil-detail precision">
        <strong>NAVLYS Précision · l'horloger suisse</strong><br>
        90% coffre · 10% poche dynamique · TP +8% · tésaurisation 50% · sweep mensuel 10%
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Capital initial -->
    <div class="ctrl-group">
      <div class="ctrl-label">
        <span>CAPITAL DE DÉPART</span>
        <span class="val"><strong id="valCapital">500</strong> €</span>
      </div>
      <input type="range" id="capital" min="500" max="1000000" step="100" value="500">
      <div class="presets">
        <span class="preset" data-target="capital" data-value="500">500€</span>
        <span class="preset" data-target="capital" data-value="1000">1 000€</span>
        <span class="preset" data-target="capital" data-value="5000">5 000€</span>
        <span class="preset" data-target="capital" data-value="10000">10 000€</span>
        <span class="preset" data-target="capital" data-value="100000">100 000€</span>
        <span class="preset" data-target="capital" data-value="1000000">1 000 000€</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- DCA mensuel -->
    <div class="ctrl-group">
      <div class="ctrl-label">
        <span>APPORT MENSUEL (DCA)</span>
        <span class="val"><strong id="valDca">100</strong> €/mois</span>
      </div>
      <input type="range" id="dca" min="0" max="5000" step="50" value="100">
      <div class="presets">
        <span class="preset" data-target="dca" data-value="0">0€</span>
        <span class="preset" data-target="dca" data-value="100">100€</span>
        <span class="preset" data-target="dca" data-value="200">200€</span>
        <span class="preset" data-target="dca" data-value="500">500€</span>
        <span class="preset" data-target="dca" data-value="1000">1 000€</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ctrl-hint">Réparti chaque mois selon le profil (Zen 97% coffre / Précision 90% / Boost 70%)</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Tésaurisation TP -->
    <div class="ctrl-group">
      <div class="ctrl-label">
        <span>SÉCURISATION DES TP</span>
        <span class="val"><strong id="valTesa">50</strong> %</span>
      </div>
      <input type="range" id="tesa" min="0" max="100" step="5" value="50">
      <div class="ctrl-hint">À chaque prise de bénéfice : % qui part au coffre, reste réinvesti dans la poche dynamique</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Sweep mensuel -->
    <div class="ctrl-group">
      <div class="ctrl-label">
        <span>SWEEP MENSUEL</span>
        <span class="val"><strong id="valSweep">10</strong> %</span>
      </div>
      <input type="range" id="sweep" min="0" max="50" step="5" value="10">
      <div class="ctrl-hint">Chaque 1er du mois : % du surplus poche dynamique versé au coffre</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Horizon -->
    <div class="ctrl-group">
      <div class="ctrl-label">
        <span>HORIZON DE SIMULATION</span>
        <span class="val"><strong id="valYears">5</strong> ans</span>
      </div>
      <input type="range" id="years" min="1" max="5" step="1" value="5">
      <div class="ctrl-hint">Données réelles disponibles : 5 ans (mai 2021 → mai 2026)</div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- ==================== RÉSULTATS ==================== -->
  <div>

    <!-- Bandeau stats -->
    <div class="results-row">
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-label">Total apporté</div>
        <div class="stat-value" id="rApport">— €</div>
        <div class="stat-sub" id="rApportSub">Capital + DCA</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-label">Valeur finale</div>
        <div class="stat-value big" id="rValeur">— €</div>
        <div class="stat-sub pos" id="rValeurSub">après horizon</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-label">Plus-value pure</div>
        <div class="stat-value pos" id="rPV">— €</div>
        <div class="stat-sub pos" id="rPVPct">+0%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-label">Drawdown max</div>
        <div class="stat-value neg" id="rDD">—%</div>
        <div class="stat-sub" id="rDDSub">pic-creux</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Onglets -->
    <div class="tabs">
      <button class="tab active" data-view="total">📈 Capital total</button>
      <button class="tab" data-view="split">🏦 Coffre vs Dynamique</button>
      <button class="tab" data-view="apport">💎 Apporté vs Possédé</button>
    </div>

    <div class="chart-box">
      <canvas id="chart" class="chart-canvas"></canvas>
    </div>

    <div class="disclaimer">
      <strong>⚓ Données utilisées :</strong> cours réels Yahoo Finance · SOL-USD, NVDA, AVGO · coffre composite SGOV+ICSH+JPST · période 2021-05 → 2026-05 · 1256 jours de bourse. Les performances passées ne préjugent pas des performances futures. Cette simulation a une vocation pédagogique. Capital non garanti, exposition crypto et actions individuelles classée risque élevé. <strong>« La meilleure façon de gagner de l'argent, c'est tout simplement de jouer avec l'argent. »</strong>
    </div>

  </div>

</div>

</div>

<script>
// ========================================================================
// NAVLYS SIMULATEUR · Moteur JS embarqué + données 5 ans
// ========================================================================
